{"tid":1437622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逃犯條例】水炮車下周一示範　立法會保安事務委員會安排成員參加","createTime":"2019-08-09T14:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T14:47:05.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"085d3bfb9c1b461919ec74efb4fc822bcdeefc29","tid":1437622,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:47:05.000Z","msg":"立法會保安事務委員會安排成員周一（12日）到粉嶺警察機動部隊總部，觀看警方水炮車（人群管理特別用途車）的示範，同時邀請監警會成員及傳媒參加。據了解，監警會主席梁定邦當日不在香港。<br />\n<br />\n周日（4日）下午，兩輛「水炮車」掛上「路面測試」字牌及以綠布裹上頂部「炮口」，沿屯門公路往荃灣方向行駛，其後駛往汀九橋，沿途有警車開路及尾隨。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190809/s00001/1565357958519/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e6%b0%b4%e7%82%ae%e8%bb%8a%e4%b8%8b%e5%91%a8%e4%b8%80%e7%a4%ba%e7%af%84-%e7%ab%8b%e6%b3%95%e6%9c%83%e4%bf%9d%e5%ae%89%e4%ba%8b%e5%8b%99%e5%a7%94%e5%93%a1%e6%9c%83%e5%ae%89%e6%8e%92%e6%88%90%e5%93%a1%e5%8f%83%e5%8a%a0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190809%2Fs00001%2F1565357958519%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25b0%25b4%25e7%2582%25ae%25e8%25bb%258a%25e4%25b8%258b%25e5%2591%25a8%25e4%25b8%2580%25e7%25a4%25ba%25e7%25af%2584-%25e7%25ab%258b%25e6%25b3%2595%25e6%259c%2583%25e4%25bf%259d%25e5%25ae%2589%25e4%25ba%258b%25e5%258b%2599%25e5%25a7%2594%25e5%2593%25a1%25e6%259c%2583%25e5%25ae%2589%25e6%258e%2592%25e6%2588%2590%25e5%2593%25a1%25e5%258f%2583%25e5%258a%25a0&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrLccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=d8ce2380\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190809%2Fs00001%2F1565357958519%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25b0%25b4%25e7%2582%25ae%25e8%25bb%258a%25e4%25b8%258b%25e5%2591%25a8%25e4%25b8%2580%25e7%25a4%25ba%25e7%25af%2584-%25e7%25ab